paragraph
 Markdown is a lightweight markup language with plain text formatting syntax. It is designed so that it can be converted to HTML and many other formats using a tool by the same name. Markdown is often used to format readme files, for writing messages in online discussion forums, and to create rich text using a plain text editor. <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown">Read more on Wikipedia...</a>

