 - the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown">Markdown Wikipedia page</a>
 - There are at least 1,023 Markdown repos on <a href="https://github.com/search?q=language:Markdown">GitHub</a>
 - file extensions for Markdown include md, livemd, markdown, mdown, mdwn, mdx, mkd, mkdn, mkdown, ronn, scd and workbook
